{"tid":1898554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞專家指全世界欠了武漢市民 並表示若感染新冠病毒想在中國治療","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T07:42:53.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6bcfd65542149f32b17028536b88715715d454","tid":1898554,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2386302/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6:%E8%8B%A5%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%83%B3%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2386302%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259E%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%3A%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2599%2582&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=40bcd4c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2386302/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6:%E8%8B%A5%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%83%B3%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82</a><br />\n結束訪問中國的世衞專家考察組組長艾爾沃德(Bruce Aylward)，再次讚揚中國應對疫情的措施，知道如何保護人民生命，表明若果自己受感染，會想在中國治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艾爾沃德昨日在北京的記者會上表示，中國的防疫隔離措施事實證明成功，他想對武漢市民表示，全世界都欠了他們。他返回瑞士日內瓦後召開記者會時，再度肯定中國應付疫情爆發採取的積極措施，認為大規模的行動改變了疫情的進程。他還表示，很多人印象中認為中國欠缺醫療設備，但今次考察看到中國動員抗疫的程度，令他知道中國如何保護人民生命。<br />\n<br />\n不過，外媒批評艾爾沃德曾前往武漢，卻未遵守隔離檢疫14天才能離境的規定，就搭機離開中國，他表示，前往中國時就算到醫院，因醫院有分乾淨、灰色及髒區，他們都待在乾淨區。<br />\n<br />\n對於出席記者會為何未戴口罩，他解釋，自己沒有感染病毒，回日內瓦前還接受檢測，因此風險很低，並指沒接觸病人、沒有與有接觸史者直接接觸、因中國政策規定所以在中國全程戴口罩、更表示自己每3秒就洗一次手。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，在中國時保持社交距離，在車上及火車上座位是一人一排、要大聲說話對方才聽的見，亦是單獨在飯店房間用餐，就算開會也是一人一張桌子開麥克風對話。"},{"pid":"62f3745d053ddd97ed84d875d419494def530cb6","tid":1898554,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報道<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=d2f1f918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&h=f38fff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=441ec784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&h=caebb208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n香港記者報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841500569600?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=d9f0ca4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&h=d0ba2080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841500569600?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/damon_pang/status/1232558018920767495?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdamon_pang%2Fstatus%2F1232558018920767495%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=94b5bd5b\" data-ef-u